-- ds.page: `serve-image` API

We store images in database, and use this api to serve them to users. Read more
about this design in the [snapshots guide](/dev/guides/snapshots/).

-- ds.h1: URL & Parameters

/page/serve-image/?slide=<id>&preview=true

-- ds.h2: `id`

This parameter will be the `id` of the `slide`. It is a required parameter.

-- ds.h2: `preview`

This parameter is optional. If it is set to `true`, the image will be served in
a smaller size. This is useful for show preview images in the editor etc.

-- end: ds.page
